  "title": "DIRECTOR HAIRSTYLIST",
  "description": "<p>KEY RESPONSIBILITIES<br /></p><ul><li>Lead and oversee all hair styling operations at a director level</li><li>Deliver advanced, high-end hair services (cutting, coloring, styling, treatments)</li><li>Set and maintain salon quality standards, techniques, and service excellence</li><li>Mentor, train, and develop junior and senior stylists</li><li>Create and implement new styling techniques, trends, and service menus</li><li>Consult with high-profile and VIP clients to ensure personalized results</li><li>Monitor hygiene, safety, and professional standards at all times</li><li>Collaborate with management on business growth, branding, and client retention</li><li>Stay updated with global hair trends, products, and technologies</li></ul><p><br />REQUIREMENTS AND QUALIFICATIONS<br /></p><ul><li>Minimum 15 years of experience as a PROFESSIONAL hair stylist</li><li><p>Proven experience at Director Stylist level</p></li><li><p>Advanced technical expertise in cutting, coloring, and hair treatments</p></li><li><p>Strong leadership, communication, and team management skills</p></li><li><p>Passion for creativity, innovation, and client satisfaction</p></li><li><p>Professional certifications in hair styling (preferred)</p></li><li><p>Excellent presentation and customer service skills</p></li></ul>",
