    "description": "<p>   ZINC SALON PTE. LTD.</p>  <p>   Located at the millenia walk, Zinc Korean Hair Salon brings you the best in a wide range of hair services. You will be impressed by the handiwork of our experienced hairstylists, whose forte includes shaping, conditioning, and treatment for pre-wedding preparations. With our professional recommendations, your can rest assured that your hair will be in perfect shape, colour and condition to suit any occasion. Expect to be at your most stunning with the least effort on your special day!</p>  ",
